Reasoning: The paper discusses the use of social media platforms to disseminate scholarly articles, which is relevant to the fields of digital libraries (cs.DL) and social media (cs.SI). The analysis of data from Web of Science and Altmetric.com involves information retrieval (cs.IR) and data mining (cs.CY). The examination of the role of source of publication in altmetric coverage level of articles may also relate to cryptography (cs.CR) in terms of ensuring the authenticity and integrity of the data.
